name: Encounter I
description: I came across this on my journey to R̶̨͈͔̝͖̱̲͔̰͎̥̩̈́̊͊̋̂̀̽̄Ḙ̴͕̟̙́̌͛͝D̵̮̫̱̣̤̝̥̬͎̤̍̇͐͆̅̀͊͒̑̚̚Ạ̵̛̰̤͓͇͖͕͉̯̰̰̔̓͐̕͠C̸̤̬͕̟̽̌̈́͌͊̔͆̇̏͑͂̕͝͝Ṯ̸͕̜͔̣̑͂͌͒̆E̸̢̧̖͇̤͙̩̥̣͇͊̑Ď̴̨̢̯̯̣͙̺͖̤̰̫̳̖̠͔̦̿̓̽̔̆̈͑͛̾͌͋͋̏̕. I don't know what it wants or if it is even alive but it made me feel a certain way.
